uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.parquetstore

Class ParquetStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.store.Store
      • uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.parquetstore.ParquetStore
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SingleUseParquetStore

    public class ParquetStore
extends Store
    An implementation of Store that uses Parquet files to store the Elements.

    It is designed to make the most of the Parquet file types by serialising the Elements using ParquetSerialisers which also allows for Gaffer objects to be stored as multiple or nested columns of primitive types.
